== 歷史 ==
157街車站首次開放時是非正式、未完工的狀態，1904年10月29日作為臨時車站服務[[耶魯大學|耶魯]]-[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞]]比賽的粉絲<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LYSVd43vZwQC|title=Under the Sidewalks of New York: The Story of the Greatest Subway System in the World|last=Cudahy|first=Brian J.|date=1995-01-01|publisher=Fordham Univ Press|isbn=9780823216185|language=en}}</ref>。

157街車站後來在1904年11月12日正式開放。此站是首次在已有的地鐵路線上加入新車站。車站的開放延後了兩個星期，主要因為車站仍有一些塗裝和抹灰尚未完成<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oJ5RAAAAYAAJ|title=Real Estate Record and Builders' Guide|date=1904-01-01|publisher=F. W. Dodge Corporation|language=en}}</ref>。

此站以南一站的[[145街車站_(IRT百老匯-第七大道線)|145街車站]]是當初的總站<ref>James Blaine Walker, [https://books.google.com/books?vid=OCLC03638541&id=lpEgAAAAMAAJ Fifty Years of Rapid Transit, 1864-1917] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?vid=OCLC03638541&id=lpEgAAAAMAAJ |date=20190610095822 }}, published 1918, pp. 162-191</ref><ref name="HISTORY.com 1904">{{cite web|url=http://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/new-york-city-subway-opens|title=New York City subway opens - Oct 27, 1904|date=1904-10-27|website=HISTORY.com|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2010-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100307191545/http://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/new-york-city-subway-opens|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在首日營運時，車站用作容許乘客前往波羅土地觀看足球比賽<ref>{{cite news|title=Subway On East Side Will Be Opened Soon: New Switching Station on West Side Nearly ready, too Football Trains On Today|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9F02E7DC113BE631A25751C1A9679D946597D6CF|accessdate=19 August 2015|publisher=New York Times|date=November 12, 1904|archive-date=2017-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411054058/https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9F02E7DC113BE631A25751C1A9679D946597D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>。從此以後，157街就成為了不途經萊諾克斯大道線列車的總站。157街總站設有讓列車調頭的設施，紓緩了96街的擠塞。1906年3月12日，IRT由157街延長至[[221街車站_(IRT百老匯-第七大道線)|221街]]<ref name="225th2">[[New_York_Times|New York Times]], [https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F40817FE355417738DDDAD0994D9405B878CF1D3 Farthest North in Town by the Interborough] {{Wayback|url=https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F40817FE355417738DDDAD0994D9405B878CF1D3 |date=20140222175336 }}, January 14, 1907, page 18</ref>。服務新延線的接駁列車以157街為總站，意味着157街以南的乘客若前往新延線需於該站轉乘<ref>{{cite web|url=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/15/1906_IRT_map_north.png|title=<!-- empty -->|accessdate=2017-04-10|archive-date=2016-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008185111/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/15/1906_IRT_map_north.png|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1906年5月30日，快車開始直通至221街，此情況不再存在<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9F00E3D9143DE733A25753C3A9639C946797D6CF|title=Express to 221st Street: Will Run In the Subway To-day–New 181st Street Station Ready.|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=2016-09-01|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914101444/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9F00E3D9143DE733A25753C3A9639C946797D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1948年，[[IRT百老匯-第七大道線|IRT百老匯-第七大道線]]由103街到238街的月台都延長至514英呎以停靠10節快車列車。過去車站只能停靠6節慢車。而月台延長分段開放。1948年4月6日，由[[103街車站_(IRT百老匯-第七大道線)|103街]]到[[迪克曼街車站_(IRT百老匯-第七大道線)|迪克曼街]]開放了月台延伸段，但[[125街車站_(IRT百老匯-第七大道線)|125街]]除外，於1948年6月11日才開放<ref name="BOT-19492">{{Cite book|url=http://hdl.handle.net/2027/mdp.39015023094926|title=Report for the three and one-half years ending June 30, 1949.|date=1949|publisher=New York City Board of Transportation}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9F0CE4D7123EE03BBC4852DFB1668383659EDE|title=MORE LONG PLATFORMS; Five Subway Stations on IRT to Accommodate 10-Car Trains|date=1948-07-10|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-03-27|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408204234/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9F0CE4D7123EE03BBC4852DFB1668383659EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

